ord":"jeopardize"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.危及，危害（to endanger)"},{"type":"text","text":"['d3epardaiz]"},{"type":"text","text":"园发音记忆：“皆怕打死”→当危及自身安全时，谁都怕死→危及"},{"type":"text","text":"compromise, hazard, imperil, jeopard"},{"type":"entry","text":"premeditate","headword":"premeditate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.预谋，预先考虑或安排（to plan，arrange,or plot in advance)"},{"type":"text","text":"[.pri:'medrtert]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：pre（预先）+medit（思考）+ale→预谋"},{"type":"entry","text":"vex","headword":"vex"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 使烦恼，使恼怒(to bring agitation to)"},{"type":"text","text":"[veks]"},{"type":"text","text":"annoy, bother, fret, irk"},{"type":"entry","text":"anterior","headword":"anterior"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.较早的，以前的（previous，earlier)"},{"type":"text","text":"[aen'trriar]"},{"type":"entry","text":"sedate","headword":"sedate"},{"type":"definition","text":"adji. 镇静的(keeping a quiet steady attitude or pace; unruffled)"},{"type":"text","text":"[sr'dert]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：sed（坐下）+ate→坐下来的→镇静的"},{"type":"text","text":"sober, staid"},{"type":"entry","text":"demotic","headword":"demotic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 民众的(of or pertaining to the people); 通俗的"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'ma:trk]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：demo（人民）+tic（--的）→民众的"},{"type":"entry","text":"sanitary","headword":"sanitary"},{"type":"text","text":"adfj (有关)卫生的，清洁的(of or relating to health)"},{"type":"text","text":"['saenateri]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：sanit（健康的）+ary→卫生的，清洁的"}]},{"number":253,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"text","text":"circumlocutionn.迁回累整的陈述(a roundabout,lengthy way of expressing sth.)"},{"type":"text","text":"[s3:rkamla'kju:[n]园词根记忆：circum（环绕，周围）+locu（说话）+tion→说话绕圈子→迁回累整的"},{"type":"text","text":"陈述"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.节俭的(frugal,thrifty)"},{"type":"entry","text":"sparing","headword":"sparing"},{"type":"text","text":"['sperin]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自spare（v节约）：注意不要和sparring（n.拳击）相混"},{"type":"entry","text":"vestigial","headword":"vestigial"},{"type":"text","text":"aoj 退化的(degraded)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ve'strdzial]"},{"type":"text","text":"rudimentary"},{"type":"entry","text":"sumptuous","headword":"sumptuous"},{"type":"text","text":"adlj.豪华的，奢侈的(extremely costly, luxurious, or magnificent)"},{"type":"text","text":"['samptfuas]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：sumpt（拿，取）+uous→（把钱）拿出去→奢侈的"},{"type":"text","text":"The sumpfuous costumes of Renaissance Italy, with their gold and silver"},{"type":"text","text":"embroidery and figured brocades, were the antithesis of Spanish sobriety, with"},{"type":"example","text":"its dark muted colors, plain short capes, and high collars edged with small ruffs."},{"type":"text","text":"deluxe, palatial"},{"type":"entry","text":"construe","headword":"construe"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 解释(to explain or interpret):翻译(to translate orally)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kan'stru]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：con（强调）+strue（看作struct，结构）→弄清结构→解释"},{"type":"entry","text":"toady","headword":"toady"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.谄媚者，马屁精（one who flatters)"},{"type":"text","text":"['taudi]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：toad（蛤）+y→像蛤一样趴在地上的人→马屁精"},{"type":"example","text":"Just as sloth is the mark of the idler, obsequiousness is the mark of the toady."},{"type":"text","text":"bootlicker, brownnoser, cringer, fawner"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.节制，限量，节省(to restrict or limit, as in amount or number)"},{"type":"entry","text":"stint","headword":"stint"},{"type":"text","text":"[stint]"},{"type":"text","text":"stint on sth.客惜"},{"type":"entry","text":"deign","headword":"deign"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.惠允（做某事)(to condescend to do sth.;stoop)：施惠于人（to condescend to"},{"type":"text","text":"[dern]"},{"type":"text","text":"give or grant)"},{"type":"text","text":"condescend"},{"type":"entry","text":"tint","headword":"tint"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 色泽(slight degree of a color) v 给淡淡地着色(to give a slight color to);染"},{"type":"text","text":"[tint]"},{"type":"entry","text":"stratify","headword":"stratify"},{"type":"definition","text":"v (使)层化(to divide or arrange into classes, castes, or social strata)"},{"type":"text","text":"['straetrfar]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：Strat（层次）+ify→（使）层化"},{"type":"entry","text":"fluctuate","headword":"fluctuate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 波动(to undulate as waves); 变动(to be continually changing)"},{"type":"text","text":"[flAktfuert]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：fluctu（波浪）+alte→波动；变动"},{"type":"entry","text":"avarice","headword":"avarice"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 贪财，贪婪(too great a desire to have wealth; cupidity)"},{"type":"text","text":"['avaris]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆发音记忆：“爱不释手”→贪婪"}]},{"number":254,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 21 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"indigent","headword":"indigent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.贫穷的，贫困的(deficient, impoverished)"},{"type":"text","text":"['indidzant]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：in（无）+dig（挖）+ent→挖不出东西→贫穷的"},{"type":"entry","text":"asunder","headword":"asunder"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.分离的（apart or separate)；化为碎片的(into pieces)adv分离地：化为碎片地"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'ssndar]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：as（好像）+under（下面）→好像在下面→分离的"},{"type":"entry","text":"mournful","headword":"mournful"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.悲伤的(feeling or expressing sorrow or grief)"},{"type":"text","text":"['m>:rnfl]"},{"type":"text","text":"doleful, dolorous, plaintive, woeful"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 晒太阳,取暖(to warm oneself pleasantly in the sunlight)"},{"type":"entry","text":"bask","headword":"bask"},{"type":"text","text":"[baesk]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：把basket去掉et，就是bask→拎着篮子晒太阳→取暖"},{"type":"entry","text":"inalienable","headword":"inalienable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 不能转让的： 不可剥夺的(not transferable to another or capable of being"},{"type":"text","text":"[rn'erlianabl]"},{"type":"text","text":"repudiated)"},{"type":"text","text":"围词根记忆：in（不)+alien（转让）+able→不能转让的"},{"type":"entry","text":"vicissitude","headword":"vicissitude"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 变迁, 兴衰(natural change or mutation visible in nature or in human affairs)"},{"type":"text","text":"[vt'sisrtu:d]"},{"type":"entry","text":"repeal","headword":"repeal"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.废除(法律)(to annul by authoritative act)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr'pi:l]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：re（相反，不）+peal（呼吁）→不呼吁→废除"},{"type":"entry","text":"inure","headword":"inure"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 使习惯于(to accustom to accept something undesirable); 生效(to become of"},{"type":"text","text":"[r'njur]"},{"type":"text","text":"advantage)"},{"type":"entry","text":"relegate","headword":"relegate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.使降级，贬滴（to send to exile;assign to oblivion)：交付，托付（torefer or"},{"type":"text","text":"['relngert]"},{"type":"text","text":"assign for decision or action)"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：re（再）+leg（选择）+ate→重新选择职位→使降级"},{"type":"entry","text":"gaudy","headword":"gaudy"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. f俗的(bright and showy)"},{"type":"text","text":"['go:di]"},{"type":"text","text":"图发音记忆：“高低”→花衣服穿得高高低低→俗丽的"},{"type":"entry","text":"exonerate","headword":"exonerate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 免除责任(to relieve from an obligation);确定无罪(to clear from guilt; absolve)"},{"type":"text","text":"[g'za:narert]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：ex（向外）+oner（负担）+ate→走出负担→免除责任"},{"type":"entry","text":"stagger","headword":"stagger"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.踝理，摇晃(to move on unsteadily)"},{"type":"text","text":"[’staegar]"},{"type":"text","text":"lurch, reel, sway, waver, wobble"},{"type":"entry","text":"infuse","headword":"infuse"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.注入，灌输(to instill; impart)：鼓励(to inspire)"},{"type":"text","text":"[in'fju:z]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：in（进入）+fus（流）+e→流进去→注入，灌输"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.平静的，安详的（marked by or suggestive of utter calm and unruffled repose"},{"type":"entry","text":"serene","headword":"serene"},{"type":"text","text":"[sa'ri:n]"},{"type":"text","text":"or quietude）;清澈的：晴朗的"},{"type":"text","text":"The paradoxical aspect of the myths about Demeter, when we consider the"},{"type":"text","text":"predominant image of her as a tranquil and serene goddess, is her agitated"},{"type":"text","text":"search for her daughter."},{"type":"entry","text":"impecunious","headword":"impecunious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.不名一文的，没钱的（having very little or no money)"},{"type":"text","text":"[,xmpr'kju:nias]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：im（无）+pecun（钱）+ious→没钱的"},{"type":"entry","text":"confine","headword":"confine"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.限制，禁闭(to keep a person or an animal in a restricted space; restrain)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kan'fain]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：con（加强）+fin（范围）+e→进入（别人）范围→限制"},{"type":"text","text":"circumscribe, delimit"},{"type":"entry","text":"disparage","headword":"disparage"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.贬低，轻藏（to speak slightingly of;depreciate;decry)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'spaerid3]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：dis（除去）+par（平等）+age→剥夺平等→贬低"}]},{"number":255,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"eulogize","headword":"eulogize"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 称费，颂扬(to praise highly in speech or writing)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ju:lad3a1z]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：eu（善，美）+log（说）+ize→说好话→称费"},{"type":"entry","text":"tawdry","headword":"tawdry"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.华而不实的，俗丽的（cheap but showy)"},{"type":"text","text":"['to:dri]"},{"type":"text","text":"tawdryclothing廉价而花哨的衣服"},{"type":"entry","text":"welter","headword":"welter"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.混乱，杂乱无章（a disordered mixture)"},{"type":"text","text":"[weltar]"},{"type":"text","text":"圈联想记忆：像一个大熔炉（melter）一样一片混乱（welter）"},{"type":"entry","text":"penchant","headword":"penchant"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.爱好，嗜好（liking)"},{"type":"text","text":"['pentfant]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：pench（看作pend，挂）+ant→对挂着一颗心→爱好"},{"type":"example","text":"Although retiring. almost self-effacing in his private life, he displays in his"},{"type":"text","text":"plays and essays a strong penchant for publicity and controversy."},{"type":"entry","text":"egoistic","headword":"egoistic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj自我中心的，自私自利的（of or relating to the sell)"},{"type":"text","text":"[i:gau'rstk]"},{"type":"text","text":"egocentric, egomaniacal, self-centered, selfish"},{"type":"entry","text":"surly","headword":"surly"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.脾气暴躁的(bad tempered);阴沉的(sullen)"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：sur（看作sir，先生）+ly→像高高在上的先生一般→牌气暴躁的"},{"type":"text","text":"['s3:rli]"},{"type":"entry","text":"hypothetical","headword":"hypothetical"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj 假设的(based on a hypothesis)"},{"type":"text","text":"[harpa'Betikl]"},{"type":"text","text":"conjectural"},{"type":"entry","text":"torpid","headword":"torpid"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 懒散的; 迟钝的(lacking in energy or vigor; dull)"},{"type":"text","text":"[to:rprd]"},{"type":"text","text":"lethargic, sluggish, stupid"},{"type":"entry","text":"slovenly","headword":"slovenly"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 不整洁的，邀退的(untidy especially in personal appearance)"},{"type":"text","text":"[slavnli]"},{"type":"text","text":"dirty"},{"type":"entry","text":"obliging","headword":"obliging"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.乐于助人的(helpful, accommodating)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'blaid3in]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆来自oblige（v.施恩惠于，帮助）"},{"type":"entry","text":"appease","headword":"appease"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.使平静，安抚（topacify orquiet)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'pi:z]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：ap（使）+pease(和平）→使平静"},{"type":"text","text":"assuage, conciliate, mollify, pacify, propitiate"},{"type":"entry","text":"jest","headword":"jest"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.笑话，俏皮话(joke) v说笑，开玩笑（to joke;be playful in speech and actions)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dzest]"},{"type":"text","text":"fleer, flout, gibe, jeer, scoff"},{"type":"entry","text":"tantalize","headword":"tantalize"},{"type":"definition","text":"v挑葱，挑逗(to tease or torment by a sight of sth. that is desired but cannot be"},{"type":"text","text":"['taentalarz]"},{"type":"text","text":"reached)"},{"type":"text","text":"圆来自希腊神话人物Tantalus（坦塔洛斯），他因泄露天机而被罚立在近下巴深的水"},{"type":"text","text":"中，口渴欲饮时水即流失；头上有果树，腹饥欲食时果子即消失。"}]},{"number":256,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 21 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"beneficent","headword":"beneficent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.慈善的，仁爱的(doing or producing good);有益的(beneficial)"},{"type":"text","text":"[br'nefrsnt]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：bene（好）+fic（做）+ent（的）→做好事的→慈善的"},{"type":"entry","text":"iridescent","headword":"iridescent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 色彩斑期的(producing a display of lustrous, rainbowlike colors)"},{"type":"text","text":"[,xrr'desnt]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：irid（看作iris，虹光）+escent（开始的）→闪着彩虹般的光的→色彩斑斓的"},{"type":"entry","text":"frugal","headword":"frugal"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 节约的，节俭的(careful and thrifty)"},{"type":"text","text":"[fru:gl]"},{"type":"entry","text":"rivalry","headword":"rivalry"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.竞争，对抗(the state of being a rival)"},{"type":"text","text":"['rarvlri]"},{"type":"text","text":"competition, contention, contest"},{"type":"entry","text":"penitent","headword":"penitent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj 悔过的，悔的(expressing regretful pain; repentant)"},{"type":"text","text":"['penitant]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：penit（看作pen，处罚）+ent→受了处罚所以后悔→悔过的"},{"type":"entry","text":"peerless","headword":"peerless"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.出类拔萃的，无可匹敌的（matchless,incomparable)"},{"type":"text","text":"[prrlas]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：peer（同等的人）+less（无）→无可匹敌的"},{"type":"entry","text":"cavil","headword":"cavil"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.挑毛病，吹毛求疵（to object when there is little reason to do so:quibble)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kaevl]"},{"type":"t