anism","headword":"sectarianism"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.宗派主义：教派意识"},{"type":"text","text":"[sek'terianrzam]"},{"type":"entry","text":"inquisitive","headword":"inquisitive"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 好奇的，好问的(inclined to ask questions; prying)：爱打听的"},{"type":"text","text":"[1n'kwizatrv]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：in（使）+quis（询问）+itive→加以询问→好奇的，好问的"},{"type":"text","text":"Excited and unafraid, the inquisitive child examined the stranger with bright-"},{"type":"text","text":"eyed curiosity."},{"type":"entry","text":"gallant","headword":"gallant"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj勇敢的，英勇的（brave and noble);献股勤的（polite and attentive to"},{"type":"text","text":"['gaelant]"},{"type":"text","text":"someone)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：gall（胆）+ant→有胆量的→勇敢的，英勇的"},{"type":"entry","text":"valiant","headword":"valiant"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.勇敢的，英勇的（courageous)"},{"type":"text","text":"['vaeliant]"},{"type":"text","text":"valorous"},{"type":"entry","text":"astounding","headword":"astounding"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 令 人震t惊B(causing astonishment or amazement)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'staundin]"},{"type":"entry","text":"chromatic","headword":"chromatic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj彩色的，五彩的(having color or colors)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kra'maetrk]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：chrom（颜色）+atic→彩色的"},{"type":"entry","text":"scorn","headword":"scorn"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.轻蔻(disrespect or derision mixed with indignation) v 轻蔻，不起(to show"},{"type":"text","text":"[sko:rn]"},{"type":"text","text":"disdain or derision)"},{"type":"text","text":"contemn, despise"},{"type":"entry","text":"cohesive","headword":"cohesive"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.凝聚的(sticking together)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kau'hi:srv]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：co（强调）+hes（粘着）+ive→有粘合力的→凝聚的"},{"type":"entry","text":"humiliate","headword":"humiliate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v 盖辱，使丢验(to hurt the pride or dignity; mortify: degrade)"},{"type":"text