go through or range over in a search)"},{"type":"entry","text":"promulgate","headword":"promulgate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v 颁布(法令)(to put a law into action or force);宣传，传播(to spread the news)"},{"type":"text","text":"['pra:mlgert]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：pro（前面）+mulg（人民）+ate→放到人民前面→宣传，传播"},{"type":"text","text":"announce, annunciate, declare, disseminate, proclaim"},{"type":"entry","text":"tarnish","headword":"tarnish"},{"type":"definition","text":"v失去光泽，嗨暗(to dull or destroy the luster by air,dust, or dirt) n. 嗨暗，无光泽"},{"type":"text","text":"['ta:rnxf]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：tam（隐藏）+ish→隐藏光泽→失去光泽，晦暗"},{"type":"entry","text":"shrug","headword":"shrug"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.耸肩(表示怀疑等)(to raise in the shoulders to express aloofness, indifference,"},{"type":"text","text":"[{rag]"},{"type":"text","text":"or uncertainty)"},{"type":"text","text":"shrugsth.off/aside不把.-当回事；对.满不在乎"},{"type":"entry","text":"tardy","headword":"tardy"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.迟延，迟到的(delayed beyond the expected or proper time);缓慢的，迟钝的"},{"type":"text","text":"['ta:rdi]"},{"type":"text","text":"(slow to act; sluggish)"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：tard（迟缓）+y→缓慢的，迟钝的"}]},{"number":259,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"exodus","headword":"exodus"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.大批离去，成群外出(a mass departure or emigration)"},{"type":"text","text":"[eksadas]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：ex（外面）+od（看作hod，路）+us→走上外出的道路→成群外出"},{"type":"entry","text":"infuriate","headword":"infuriate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.使恼怒，激怒（to enrage）"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：in（进入）+furi(看作fury，狂怒）+ate→进入狂怒→使恼怒，激怒"},{"type":"text","text":"[in'fjuriert]"},{"type":"entry","text":"irate","headword":"irate"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 发怒的(angry. incensed)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ar'rert]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：i（我）+rate（责骂）→我被责骂了→发怒的"},{"type":"entry","text":"stilted","headword":"stilted"},{"type":"text","text":"adj（文章、谈话）不自然的：夸张的（pompous）"},{"type":"text","text":"['strltrd]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自stit（n.高跷）"},{"type":"entry","text":"remorse","headword":"remorse"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 惯悔，悔恨(a gnawing distress; self-reproach)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr'mo:rs]"},{"type":"text","text":"固词根记忆：re（反）+mors咬）+e→反过去咬自己→梅恨"},{"type":"text","text":"Although remorse is usually thought to spring from regret for having done"},{"type":"example","text":"something wrong. it may be that its origin is the realization that one's own nature"},{"type":"text","text":"is irremediably flawed."},{"type":"text","text":"compunction, contriteness, contrition, penance"},{"type":"text","text":"penitence"},{"type":"entry","text":"unwonted","headword":"unwonted"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj不寻常的，不习惯的(unusual,unaccustomed)"},{"type":"text","text":"[An'wauntid]"},{"type":"text","text":"stride"},{"type":"entry","text":"stride","headword":"stride"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 大步行走(to move with or as if with long steps)"},{"type":"text","text":"[strard]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：st+ride（骑自行车）→走得像骑自行车一样快→"},{"type":"text","text":"大步行走"},{"type":"entry","text":"insurgent","headword":"insurgent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.叛乱的，起义的（rebellious)n.叛乱分子(a person engaged in insurgent"},{"type":"text","text":"[n'ss:rdzant]"},{"type":"text","text":"activity)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：in（使）+surg（升起）+ent→使波涛涌→叛乱的"},{"type":"entry","text":"septic","headword":"septic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj 腐败的(of, relating to, or causing putrefaction);脓毒性的(relating to"},{"type":"text","text":"[septrk]"},{"type":"text","text":"involving., caused by, or affected with sepsis)"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：sept(烂）+ic→腐败的"},{"type":"entry","text":"potent","headword":"potent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.强有力的，有影响力的，有权力的（having or wielding force，authority，or"},{"type":"text","text":"['pautnt]"},{"type":"text","text":"influence);有效力的，有效能的（exerting or capable of exerting strong"},{"type":"text","text":"physiological or chemical effects)"},{"type":"entry","text":"incense","headword":"incense"},{"type":"text","text":"['rnsens] n. 香味(any pleasant fragrance)"},{"type":"text","text":"[In’sens] v. 激(to arouse the wrath of)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：in（进入）+cens（看作cand，发光）+e→焚烧→点燃怒气→激怒"},{"type":"text","text":"enrage, infuriate, madlden"},{"type":"entry","text":"agitate","headword":"agitate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.鼓动，煸动（to argue publicly or campaign for/against sth.)：使不安，"},{"type":"text","text":"['edsrtert]"},{"type":"text","text":"使焦虑(to cause anxiety)"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：ag（做）+itate（表示不断的动作）→使不断地做→鼓动，煸动"},{"type":"entry","text":"brassy","headword":"brassy"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj厚脸皮的，无礼的(brazen， insolent)"},{"type":"text","text":"[braesi]"},{"type":"text","text":"固词根记忆：brass（黄铜）+y→脸皮像黄铜一样厚→厚脸皮的"}]},{"number":260,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 21 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"abstain","headword":"abstain"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 禁绝，放弃(to refrain deliberately and often with an effort of self-denial from an"},{"type":"text","text":"[ab'stern]"},{"type":"text","text":"action or practice)"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：abs（不）+tain（拿住）→不拿住→放弃"},{"type":"entry","text":"wilt","headword":"wilt"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 凋谢，枯菱(to lose vigor from lack of water)"},{"type":"text","text":"[wzlt]"},{"type":"text","text":"mummify, shrivel, wither"},{"type":"entry","text":"monochromatic","headword":"monochromatic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 单色的(having only one color)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ma:nakrau'maetik]图词根记忆：mono（单一）+chrom（颜色）+atic→单色的"},{"type":"text","text":"Most people who are color-blind actually can distinguish several colors; some,"},{"type":"text","text":"however, have a truly monochromatic view of a world all in shades of gray."},{"type":"entry","text":"giddy","headword":"giddy"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.轻浮的，轻率的（not serious;frivolous)"},{"type":"text","text":"['grd]"},{"type":"text","text":"flighty, frothy"},{"type":"entry","text":"adorn","headword":"adorn"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 装饰(to decorate; beautify)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'do:rn]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：ad（去）+orn（装饰）→装饰"}]}]}